CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 2, 2006

[Cite as 05/02/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2158.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2005-1228. O’Connor v. Cleveland Clinic Found.

Cuyahoga App. No. 84219,161 Ohio App.3d 43, 2005-Ohio-2328. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion for a continuance of oral argument,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion is denied.
